# Newsletter delivery log — written by /api/webhooks/resend on every Resend
# event. Lives in /public for the cron to commit later if desired, but we
# gitignore it for now to keep the repo small. If you want historical
# analytics, remove this line.
public/newsletter-events.jsonl

# Dropbox sync conflict files — created when Dropbox detects a write race
# while syncing the repo (e.g. between an editor save and a git checkout).
# Pattern: `<name> (<user>'s conflicted copy YYYY-MM-DD[ HH-MM-SS]).<ext>`.
# Harmless on disk but easy to commit by accident if you `git add .`.
*conflicted copy*
